ise was born the tenth day of November, 1882. Gwilym Samuel - Rhys born the sixteenth of November 1884. Joseph Louis Rhys born the twelfth of May 1886. The above Joseph died the twenty-fourth day of August, 1887. Catherine Ann Rhys born March the seventh 
