We didn't have a big garden. No. But my mother's - my father used to put - bit of parsley and thyme you know, no potatoes, no. 'Cos our garden was very small.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11172311 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10514204\charrsid12156020 Did they buy any fruit?
