e you know - her mother was living there, would I go down the Britannia, that was a public house you know, to fetch her twopennyworth of - what was it now - Burton. And I didn't know what it was see. And my mother said to me, where have you been? And I sa
id, down to Mrs John to go a message for her. What did you bring back {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Burton{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 for her. You go to the Band of Hope remember, she said to me. Well no matter, she said - I said to her, well I only went in and asked for it. My mother said, you are not to go she 
said. Going on then, she gave me a banana once - and I took it home and my father - and I said to my father - what is that dad, I said to him. Where did you get it, he said. From Mrs John. The peel, he said to me, throw it in the bin and don't eat it. He 
s
aid they weren't fit to eat and they aren't fit either, no. No. Nor he wouldn't - my mother used to buy a cucumber for my youngest sister, she used to like it you know. And she said - he - my father always used to turn to me. And - he'd say the same about
 
a - a cucumber. Peel it and throw it out. He said they weren't fit to eat. I never a cucumber - myself in my life. And my husband said to me - I like a cucumber. Well I'm not buying it, I said. No. However - if my father - my mother tell my father, go to 
bed William, the girls want to wash their hair. My father wouldn't go. A shile now Mary, he said to have a little smoke, he used to smoke - sevenpence worth a week, of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Franklins
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} tobacco, sevenpence worth mind. He'd sit in the armchair and perhaps I'd be the
re. He said, I will settle down here on the stool. We had a little stool, used to sit on the stool, now when we are grown up nearly you know. And he used to fill his pipe, we had to turn round to that part then, right around, until we were dry. You see -

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11172311 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10514204\charrsid12156020 He'd rub your hair?
