 my mother used to always - often buy a rabbits, and she used to stew it sometimes, boil it other times, and roast it then with a piece of pork.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11172311 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10514204\charrsid12156020 You wouldn't have it from poaching? She'd always buy it?
